The evidence with the title 'Turkey's image in Arab world better than other powers - Daily Sabah ' says Mar 24, 2017  ... The 2016 Arab Opinion survey shows that Turkey 's image in the Arab world is far from its heyday prior to the Arab Spring , yet, it is still positive when compared to other global and regional  ... Among the countries surveyed , Turkey is the only country that is perceived positively by the majority of Arab people . 
